                     <interp inst="t18560303-365-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="wounding"></interp>, maliciously cutting and wounding <persName id="t18560303-name-377" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18560303-name-377" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
